summary: This document is an overdraft notice from Fifth Third Bank addressed to Vickers Investments LLC, detailing an overdraft occurrence on November 4, 2013. It outlines the account's balance, fees waived, and urges the account holder to make a deposit to avoid further fees.

persons.name: Phili Fintchre
persons.context: Phili Fintchre is mentioned as the Relationship Manager for Vickers Investments LLC, responsible for managing the account.

persons.name: P. Brian Moore
persons.context: P. Brian Moore is identified as the Senior Vice President at Fifth Third Bank, signing off on the overdraft notice.

events.title: Overdraft Occurrence
events.description: Vickers Investments LLC's account was overdrawn by $211.48.

keyFacts: Vickers Investments LLC had an overdraft of $211.48 on November 4, 2013.
Fifth Third Bank waived a $37.00 overdraft fee as a courtesy.
The account had a beginning balance of $5,118.57 on November 4, 2013.
The document includes a summary of account activity and urges immediate action to avoid further overdrafts.
Phili Fintchre and P. Brian Moore are the bank representatives mentioned in the notice.
